HEADWORD: Debtee
<hw>Debt*ee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>One
to whom a debt is due; creditor; -- correlative to
<xex>debtor</xex>.</def> <rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

